{"questionId":"1362ccde","correctAnswer":"35","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Solve the system by substitution","content":"Substitute $y=4x+1$ into $4y=15x-8$: $$4(4x+1)=15x-8 \\Rightarrow 16x+4=15x-8 \\Rightarrow x=-12.$$ Then $y=4(-12)+1=-47$."},{"title":"Find $x - y$","content":"So $x-y=-12-(-47)=35$. The answer is <strong>35</strong>."}]}